item.title: About Me
item.description: 🙋🏽‍♂️ My name is Mohneesh Sreegirisetty. I completed my B.Tech from IIIT Nuzvid in 2019. I am very interested in Machine Learning / Artificial Intelligence . Programs that can think for themselves and take decisions based on its knowledge (or without the knowledge) is very fascinating indeed. Hence I aspire to be a data scientist.I have an in-depth knowledge of how various machine learning algorithms work and am pretty confident in my coding skills.
